# Common ignore patterns
*~
.github
.DS_Store
.svn
.cvs
*.bak
*.swp
Thumbs.db

# Node / NPM (global ignore for all folders)
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# Env files
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Optional lockfiles (uncomment if you don't want them committed)
# **/package-lock.json
# **/yarn.lock
# **/pnpm-lock.yaml

